/// Product subcategory dimension table providing detailed classification within product categories. Acts as a bridge between high-level categories and individual products. Essential for granular product analysis and enables hierarchical navigation from category to subcategory level for detailed business insights.
table 'Product Subcategories Lookup'
	lineageTag: e66a91be-cc07-4824-8388-6d18937d8353

	column ProductSubcategoryKey
